.SH "NAME"
Linux::MemInfo \- Perl extension for accessing /proc/meminfo
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.IX Header "SYNOPSIS"
.Vb 1
\&  use Linux::MemInfo;
.Ve
.SH "ABSTRACT"
.IX Header "ABSTRACT"
.Vb 2
\&  This module will allow you to easily extract the fields out of the
\&  /proc/meminfo file.  All of the fields are stored in a hash.
.Ve
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
